Thanks for checking out Apples!

A small C++/raylib arcade game where you catch falling apples before time runs out.

## Features
- Falling apples
- Score + high score saving
- Timer system
- Background music + sound effects
- Restart system
- Player movement + collision

## Screenshot
(Coming Soon)

## Linux Build
Compile with:
```bash
g++ *.cpp -o apple-catcher -lraylib -lGL -lm -lpthread -ldl -lrt -lX11 -lasound

## Run With
./apple-catcher

## Windows
Not officially tested yet.
Can likely be compiled using raylib + MinGW.

